This project hits the Bored API

First clone the repo using 
```bash
git clone
```


the first thing you need to do after you clone the repository is to create your virtual environment
Windows command: 
```bash 
python3 -m venv .venv
.venv\Scripts\activate 
```
Mac:
```bash
python3 -m venv .venv
source venv/bin/activate
```

After you have your virtual env created execute the command below to get all the necessary dependencies 
```bash
pip install -r requirements.txt
```
Run the script and see how to use the CLI tool

```bash
python3 .\src\hit_api.py --help
```
Example of how to use one of the commands
```bash
python3 .\src\hit_api.py busy_work 
```
